WEBVTT

00:08:27.864 --> 00:08:31.067
And I wanted to say no to that.

00:08:31.487 --> 00:08:34.722
CA: Talk a bit more about that,
because on the face of it,

00:08:34.746 --> 00:08:39.531
many people's gut reaction is to say,
"Islam, you know, hair-covering ...

00:08:39.555 --> 00:08:42.018
What could be more oppressive than that?"

00:08:42.042 --> 00:08:46.645
That religion is assumed to be one
in which women are oppressed.

00:08:46.669 --> 00:08:50.807
You found an argument and a belief
that was actually the opposite of that.

00:08:50.831 --> 00:08:52.270
Talk more about that.

00:08:53.203 --> 00:08:54.798
DM: Well, I think it's important,

00:08:54.822 --> 00:08:59.369
yet it's so hard to talk right
about the hair covering,

00:08:59.393 --> 00:09:02.186
and why it, for me, felt very empowering,